Package: RforEvolution
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Evolutionary Selection Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Taylor Papke
Maintainer: Taylor Papke <taylor.papke@example.com>
Description: Provides a comprehensive suite of functions for estimating linear, 
    quadratic, and correlational selection gradients. Includes tools for 
    visualizing correlated fitness surfaces and population-level adaptive landscapes.
